      • fromString

        public static final Exceptional<Pitch> fromString(java.lang.String pitchString)
        Any input in the form - ${key}${octave} - ${key}${octave}(${program number}) is accepted and converted into a Pitch. ${program number} is intentionally not accepted because #fromProgramNumber exists and should be used instead.
        Parameters:
        pitchString - the string to be parsed
        Returns:
        an optional Pitch representative of the pitchString
